A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 State Government – Office of the Correctional Ombudsman – Juvenile Justice
3 Monitor – Appointment
4 FOR the purpose of providing that the Director of Juvenile Justice Monitoring is appointed
5 by the Correctional Ombudsman to serve a certain term; requiring the appointment
6 of the Director of Juvenile Justice Monitoring to be subject to the advice and consent
7 of the Senate under certain circumstances; and generally relating to the Juvenile
8 Justice Monitoring Unit.
